MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Major UI architecture redesign:
- Top navigation bar with BE:CURIOUS branding (Background Dark #3D365C)
- Two theme tabs: Home Visits (Teal accent) and Pipeline (Orange accent)
- Each theme is a full-screen panel with its own contextual toolbar
- Home Visits toolbar: stats, auto-schedule, warnings, reports, teachers, cars + sub-tabs (Daily/Week/Audit)
- Pipeline toolbar: SOP 4.6.4 label + sub-tabs (Dashboard/Kanban)
- Pipeline dashboard: KPI cards, 5 Weekly Numbers, enrollment funnel chart, source breakdown, recent activity
- Shared buttons in top nav: Students, Import, Export, Settings, Help
- Help page with categorized guides (Home Visits / Pipeline / Shared sections)
- CSS custom properties for theme accent switching via data-active-theme attribute
- Brand colors: Ambition Purple #6A5FA8, People Orange #E87C50, Calming Teal #4DBFAD, Young Green #7ECB8F, Background Beige #F0EDE5, Background Dark #3D365C
